f.p_discharge_type.description:
Location or type of water body into which the TRI chemical is being discharged. Provide a coded value to limit results to facilities discharging to a specific discharge type. 
- SW = Surface waters; 
- STP = Sewage treatment plants;
- SWONLY = ONLY to surface waters;
- STPONLY = ONLY to sewage treatment plants

