f.p_imp_sw.description:
Surface Water Impairment Flag. Provide a coded value to filter on facilities potentially contributing to surface water impairments.
- Y =Only include facilities that discharge to impaired surface waters;
- POLL =Only include facilities that discharge to impaired surface waters and discharge one or more pollutants that are potentially causing the impairment (you must also provide p_imp_sw_source with this value).

